# Proprietary media support

Vivaldi does not directly bundle any library with support for
"proprietary media" (H.264/AAC), since this would make redistribution of
the output package difficult (due to software patent licensing).
Instead, the package vivaldi-altffmpeg (available as a SlackBuild) will
handle this for you.

To test proprietary media works as expected go to the following page and
attempt to play the video:

<https://help.vivaldi.com/desktop/media/html5-proprietary-media-on-linux/>
